OL,3,CTrick or treat? Illegal additives
OL,4,Cfound in some Halloween sweets
OL,6,FIllegal sweets packed with additives
OL,7,Fthat could harm children's health are
OL,8,Fbeing sold across the country, as ITV
OL,9,FNews' Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FIn the run-up to Halloween, people are
OL,13,Fbeing warned about illegal sweets
OL,14,Fpacked with additives that could harm
OL,15,Fkids' health.
OL,17,FAmerican confectionary which does not
OL,18,Fcomply with UK legislation has been
OL,19,Fseized in several locations across the
OL,20,FUK.
