OL,3,CTrick or treat? Illegal additives
OL,4,Cfound in some Halloween sweets
OL,6,FExperts say the products contain
OL,7,Funauthorised additives - some linked
OL,8,Fwith hyperactivity and "potentially
OL,9,Fcancer-causing chemicals".
OL,11,FOn Monday, Professor Robin May, the
OL,12,FFood Standards Agency's chief
OL,13,Fscientific advisor, told ITV News:
OL,14,F"They may contain additives that are
OL,15,Feither not permitted at all in the UK
OL,16,For are permitted but at much lower
OL,17,Flevels.
