OL,3,CTrick or treat? Illegal additives
OL,4,Cfound in some Halloween sweets
OL,6,F"There's not a short-term risk but
OL,7,Fover the long term if you continue to
OL,8,Fconsume these there might be a health
OL,9,Frisk which includes things like
OL,10,Fpotential cancer-causing chemicals."
OL,12,FSome of the sweet brands involved have
OL,13,Fperfectly legal versions sold in the
OL,14,FUK - but the ones being seized are
OL,15,Fdifferent because they contain
OL,16,Fingredients banned in this country.
OL,17,FOfficials say the American
OL,18,Fmanufacturers never intended them to
OL,19,Fbe sold here.
