OL,3,CTrick or treat? Illegal additives
OL,4,Cfound in some Halloween sweets
OL,6,FITV News has spoken to environmental
OL,7,Fhealth officers and Trading Standards
OL,8,Fprofessionals and has been told that
OL,9,Fthousands of these sweets have been
OL,10,Fseized.
OL,12,FWhen we looked at a sample of shops
OL,13,Fspecialising in American confectionary
OL,14,Fwe found examples of products
OL,15,Fcontaining the banned substances.
OL,17,FSweets have become part of the
OL,18,FHalloween tradition - but some are
OL,19,Fscarier than others.
